{"tid":786704,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"打工仔點樣自製健康飲食???","createTime":"2018-08-20T06:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T11:27:56.000Z","uid":196751,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f998c037c4daa3a425bbf7de4d6c7e88a2b258e3","tid":786704,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"我係一個大肥仔,接近30,但係已經有兩高<br />\n平時返9收6,返到屋企都7點<br />\n自己一個住又要做家務,又要打下機<br />\n根本好難好好咁控制飲食<br />\n<br />\n首先,無精神去煮已經係一個大問題<br />\n我自己試滾水煮菜煮雞,落少少豉油吊味<br />\n個食量我就唔係好減,一條友食兩斤菜,一盒300克雞胸一餐<br />\n朝早就煎隻蛋,中午就食夜晚煮定既蕃茄雞肉炒蛋<br />\n<br />\n如是者兩星期斷斷續續加埋都食左6日,星期六日直頭唔想郁<br />\n又試過買出面一d健康餐,叮返就食得<br />\n係好食呀,差唔多8,90蚊一餐,個量又少.....<br />\n<br />\n巴絲有無咩好方法分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf6371de8b22fb08877335e311edcc6d76c29ce","tid":786704,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5523fc566e465edfb3aba31f418f9501e67238","tid":786704,"uid":196459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"好吸引呀 自己一個住又係肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bab5642d189dc1590b623240559852d7d1f14d7","tid":786704,"uid":45007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:35:33.000Z","msg":"自己買齊料meal prep3.4日 甚至一星期<br />\n有心實做到"},{"pid":"cc7d6da8a1d0f0c8acd6e7006d14e4f3ae31bdb6","tid":786704,"uid":196751,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"4bab5642d189dc1590b623240559852d7d1f14d7","tid":786704,"uid":45007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:35:33.000Z","msg":"自己買齊料meal prep3.4日 甚至一星期<br />\n有心實做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"呢個post最大難題係點樣解決又想簡單又想keep得長遠既健康飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n